#. leap/yast2/summary
msgid "YaST2 Main Package"
msgstr "Paket Utama YaST2"

#. leap/yast2/description
msgid ""
"This package contains scripts and data needed for SUSE Linux installation "
"with YaST2"
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi skrip dan data yang diperlukan untuk instalasi SUSE Linux "
"dengan YaST2"

#. leap/yast2-adcommon-python/summary
msgid "Common code for the yast python ad modules"
msgstr "Kode umum untuk modul yast python ad"

#. leap/yast2-adcommon-python/description
msgid ""
"Common code shared by the yast2-aduc, yast2-adsi, and yast2-gpmc modules."
msgstr ""
"Kode umum yang digunakan bersama oleh modul yast2-aduc, yast2-adsi, dan "
"yast2-gpmc."

#. leap/yast2-add-on/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Add-On media installation code"
msgstr "YaST2 - Kode instalasi media Add-On"

#. leap/yast2-add-on/description
msgid "This package contains YaST Add-On media installation code."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi kode instalasi media Add-On YaST."

#. leap/yast2-adsi/summary
msgid "Active Directory Compatible Service Interfaces Editor"
msgstr "Editor Active Directory Compatible Service Interfaces"

#. leap/yast2-adsi/description
msgid ""
"The ADSI Edit for YaST module provides tools for viewing and modifying an "
"LDAP tree."
msgstr ""
"Modul ADSI Edit untuk YaST menyediakan alat untuk melihat dan memodifikasi "
"pohon LDAP."

#. leap/yast2-aduc/summary
msgid "Active Directory Users and Computers for YaST"
msgstr "Active Directory Users and Computers untuk YaST"

#. leap/yast2-aduc/description
msgid ""
"The Active Directory Users and Computers for YaST module provides tools for "
"creating and modifying Users, Groups, and Computer objects in Active "
"Directory."
msgstr ""
"Modul Active Directory Users and Computers untuk YaST menyediakan alat untuk "
"membuat dan memodifikasi objek Pengguna, Grup, dan Komputer di Active "
"Directory."

#. leap/yast2-alternatives/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Manage Update-alternatives switching"
msgstr "YaST2 - Pengelolaan pengalihan Update-alternatives"

#. leap/yast2-alternatives/description
msgid "A YaST2 module to manage update alternatives switching"
msgstr "Modul YaST2 untuk mengelola pengalihan update alternatives"

#. leap/yast2-apparmor/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Plugins for AppArmor Profile Management"
msgstr "YaST2 - Plugin untuk Manajemen Profil AppArmor"

#. leap/yast2-apparmor/description
msgid "YaST2 forms and components for the management of AppArmor profiles."
msgstr "Formulir dan komponen YaST2 untuk pengelolaan profil AppArmor."

#. leap/yast2-audit-laf/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Configuration of Linux Auditing (LAF)"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Linux Auditing (LAF)"

#. leap/yast2-audit-laf/description
msgid ""
"This module allows the configuration of the audit daemon as well as to add "
"rules for the audit subsystem."
msgstr ""
"Modul ini memungkinkan konfigurasi audit daemon serta penambahan aturan "
"untuk subsistem audit."

#. leap/yast2-auth-client/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Centralised System Authentication Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Otentikasi Sistem Terpusat"

#. leap/yast2-auth-client/description
msgid ""
"With this YaST2 module you may configure centralised system authentication, "
"on a single or multipe network domains."
msgstr ""
"Dengan modul YaST2 ini Anda dapat mengonfigurasi otentikasi sistem terpusat, "
"pada satu atau beberapa domain jaringan."

#. leap/yast2-auth-server/summary
msgid "A tool for creating identity management server instances"
msgstr "Alat untuk membuat instance server manajemen identitas"

#. leap/yast2-auth-server/description
msgid ""
"The program assists system administrators to create new directory server and "
"Kerberos server instances that help to maintain centralised user identity "
"database for a network."
msgstr ""
"Program ini membantu administrator sistem untuk membuat instance server "
"direktori dan server Kerberos baru yang membantu memelihara basis data "
"identitas pengguna terpusat untuk sebuah jaringan."

#. leap/yast2-boot-server/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Network Booting and Wake-On-Lan Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Network Booting dan Wake-On-Lan"

#. leap/yast2-boot-server/description
msgid "YaST2 module for network booting and Wake-On-Lan."
msgstr "Modul YaST2 untuk network booting dan Wake-On-Lan."

#. leap/yast2-bootloader/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Bootloader Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Bootloader"

#. leap/yast2-bootloader/description
msgid "This package contains the YaST2 component for bootloader configuration."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi bootloader."

#. leap/yast2-devtools/yast2-buildtools/summary
msgid "Minimal set of tools needed to build yast module"
msgstr "Perangkat dasar minimal yang diperlukan untuk membangun modul yast"

#. leap/yast2-devtools/yast2-buildtools/description
msgid ""
"Scripts and templates required for rebuilding the existing YaST2 modules and "
"components (both ruby and C++)."
msgstr ""
"Skrip dan templat yang diperlukan untuk membangun ulang modul dan komponen "
"YaST2 yang ada (baik ruby maupun C++)."

#. leap/yast2-caasp/summary
msgid "YaST2 - CaaSP Module"
msgstr "YaST2 - Modul CaaSP"

#. leap/yast2-caasp/description
msgid ""
"Containers as a Service Platform (CaaSP) and openSUSE Kubic specific module."
msgstr ""
"Modul khusus Containers as a Service Platform (CaaSP) dan openSUSE Kubic."

#. leap/yast2-cio/summary
msgid "YaST2 - IO Channel management"
msgstr "YaST2 - Manajemen Kanal IO"

#. leap/yast2-cio/description
msgid "Provides interface for blacklisting and unblocking IO channels"
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan antarmuka untuk memasukkan ke daftar hitam dan membuka blokir "
"kanal IO"

#. leap/yast2-cluster/summary
msgid "Configuration of cluster"
msgstr "Konfigurasi kluster"

#. leap/yast2-configuration-management/summary
msgid "YaST2 - YaST Configuration Management"
msgstr "YaST2 - Manajemen Konfigurasi YaST"

#. leap/yast2-configuration-management/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the YaST2 component for Configuration Management "
"Provisioning."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk Provisioning Manajemen Konfigurasi."

#. leap/yast2-control-center/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Control Center"
msgstr "YaST2 - Pusat Kontrol"

#. leap/yast2-control-center/description
msgid "This package contains the menu selection component for YaST2."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen pemilihan menu untuk YaST2."

#. leap/yast2-control-center/yast2-control-center-qt/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Control Center (Qt Version)"
msgstr "YaST2 - Pusat Kontrol (Versi Qt)"

#. leap/yast2-control-center/yast2-control-center-qt/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the menu selection component for YaST2 using the Qt "
"toolkit."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi komponen pemilihan menu untuk YaST2 menggunakan toolkit Qt."

#. leap/yast2-core/summary
#. leap/yast2-core/yast2-core-devel/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Core Libraries"
msgstr "YaST2 - Pustaka Inti"

#. leap/yast2-core/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the scanner, parser, and interpreter runtime library "
"for the YCP scripting language used in YaST2."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi pustaka runtime pemindai, pengurai, dan interpreter untuk "
"bahasa skrip YCP yang digunakan di YaST2."

#. leap/yast2-core/yast2-core-devel/description
msgid ""
"This package contains include and documentation files for developing "
"applications using the YaST2 YCP interpreter."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi berkas include dan dokumentasi untuk mengembangkan aplikasi "
"yang menggunakan interpreter YCP YaST2."

#. leap/yast2-country/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Country Settings (Language, Keyboard, and Timezone)"
msgstr "YaST2 - Pengaturan Negara (Bahasa, Papan Ketik, dan Zona Waktu)"

#. leap/yast2-country/description
msgid ""
"Country specific data and configuration modules (language, keyboard, "
"timezone) for yast2."
msgstr ""
"Data spesifik negara dan modul konfigurasi (bahasa, papan ketik, zona waktu) "
"untuk yast2."

#. leap/yast2-country/yast2-country-data/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Data files for Country settings"
msgstr "YaST2 - Berkas Data untuk Pengaturan Negara"

#. leap/yast2-country/yast2-country-data/description
msgid ""
"Data files for yast2-country together with the most often used API functions "
"(Language module)"
msgstr ""
"Berkas data untuk yast2-country beserta fungsi API yang paling sering "
"digunakan (modul Bahasa)"

#. leap/yast2-devtools/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Development Tools"
msgstr "YaST2 - Perangkat Pengembangan"

#. leap/yast2-devtools/description
msgid "Scripts and templates for developing YaST2 modules and components."
msgstr "Skrip dan templat untuk mengembangkan modul dan komponen YaST2."

#. leap/yast2-dhcp-server/summary
msgid "YaST2 - DHCP Server Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Server DHCP"

#. leap/yast2-dhcp-server/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the YaST2 component for DHCP server configuration."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi server DHCP."

#. leap/yast2-dns-manager/summary
msgid "Samba Internal DNS Manager"
msgstr "Pengelola DNS Internal Samba"

#. leap/yast2-dns-manager/description
msgid ""
"DNS Manager for the Internal Samba Active Directory Domain Controller DNS "
"server."
msgstr ""
"Pengelola DNS untuk server DNS Internal Samba Active Directory Domain "
"Controller."

#. leap/yast2-dns-server/summary
msgid "YaST2 - DNS Server Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Server DNS"

#. leap/yast2-dns-server/description
msgid "This package contains the YaST2 component for DNS server configuration."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi server DNS."

#. leap/yast2-docker/summary
msgid "YaST2 - GUI for docker management"
msgstr "YaST2 - GUI untuk manajemen docker"

#. leap/yast2-docker/description
msgid "Provides easy to use GUI for running docker containers."
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan GUI yang mudah digunakan untuk menjalankan kontainer docker."

#. leap/yast2-drbd/summary
msgid "YaST2 - DRBD Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi DRBD"

#. leap/yast2-drbd/description
msgid ""
"YaST2 - Configuration of Distributed Replicated Block Devices. With this "
"module you can configure a distributed storage system, frequently used on "
"high availability (HA) clusters."
msgstr ""
"YaST2 - Konfigurasi Distributed Replicated Block Devices. Dengan modul ini "
"Anda dapat mengonfigurasi sistem penyimpanan terdistribusi, yang sering "
"digunakan pada kluster high availability (HA)."

#. leap/yast2-fcoe-client/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Configuration of Fibre Channel over Ethernet"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Fibre Channel over Ethernet"

#. leap/yast2-fcoe-client/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the YaST2 component for the Fibre Channel over "
"Ethernet (FCoE) configuration."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi Fibre Channel over "
"Ethernet (FCoE)."

#. leap/yast2-firewall/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Firewall Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Firewall"

#. leap/yast2-firewall/description
msgid "A YaST2 module to be used for configuring a firewall."
msgstr "Modul YaST2 yang digunakan untuk mengonfigurasi firewall."

#. leap/yast2-firstboot/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Initial System Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Sistem Awal"

#. leap/yast2-firstboot/description
msgid ""
"The YaST firstboot utility runs after installation is completed.  It guides "
"the user through a series of steps that allows for easier configuration of "
"the machine.\n"
"\n"
"YaST firstboot does not run by default and has\tto be configured to run by "
"the user or the system administrator. It is useful for image deployments "
"where the system in the image is completely configured, however some last "
"steps like root password and user logins have to be created to personalize "
"the system."
msgstr ""
"Utilitas YaST firstboot berjalan setelah instalasi selesai. Utilitas ini "
"memandu pengguna melalui serangkaian langkah yang memungkinkan konfigurasi "
"mesin yang lebih mudah.\n"
"\n"
"YaST firstboot tidak berjalan secara default dan harus dikonfigurasi untuk "
"berjalan oleh pengguna atau administrator sistem. Ini berguna untuk "
"penerapan citra (image) di mana sistem dalam citra tersebut sudah "
"terkonfigurasi sepenuhnya, namun beberapa langkah terakhir seperti kata "
"sandi root dan login pengguna harus dibuat untuk mempersonalisasi sistem."

#. leap/yast2-firstboot/yast2-firstboot-wsl/summary
#. leap/yast2-firstboot/yast2-firstboot-wsl/description
msgid "YaST2 firstboot settings for WSL images"
msgstr "Pengaturan YaST2 firstboot untuk citra WSL"

#. leap/yast2-ftp-server/summary
msgid "YaST2 - FTP configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi FTP"

#. leap/yast2-ftp-server/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the YaST2 component for FTP configuration. It can "
"configure vsftpd."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi FTP. Paket ini dapat "
"mengonfigurasi vsftpd."

#. leap/yast2-geo-cluster/summary
msgid "Configuration of booth"
msgstr "Konfigurasi booth"

#. leap/yast2-gpmc/summary
msgid "Group Policy Management Console for YaST"
msgstr "Konsol Manajemen Kebijakan Grup untuk YaST"

#. leap/yast2-gpmc/description
msgid ""
"The Group Policy Management console for YaST provides tools for creating and "
"modifying Group Policy Objects in Active Directory."
msgstr ""
"Konsol Manajemen Kebijakan Grup untuk YaST menyediakan alat untuk membuat "
"dan memodifikasi Objek Kebijakan Grup di Active Directory."

#. leap/yast2-hardware-detection/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Hardware Detection Interface"
msgstr "YaST2 - Antarmuka Deteksi Perangkat Keras"

#. leap/yast2-hardware-detection/description
msgid "This package contains the hardware detection library for YaST2."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi pustaka deteksi perangkat keras untuk YaST2."

#. leap/yast2-http-server/summary
msgid "YaST2 - HTTP Server Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Server HTTP"

#. leap/yast2-http-server/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the YaST2 component for HTTP server (Apache2) "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi server HTTP (Apache2)."

#. leap/yast2-installation/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Installation Parts"
msgstr "YaST2 - Bagian Instalasi"

#. leap/yast2-installation/description
msgid "System installation code as present on installation media."
msgstr "Kode instalasi sistem seperti yang ada pada media instalasi."

#. leap/yast2-installation-control/summary
msgid "YaST2 - RNG schema for installation control files"
msgstr "YaST2 - Skema RNG untuk berkas kontrol instalasi"

#. leap/yast2-installation-control/description
msgid ""
"This package contains RNG schema for validating the installation control "
"files."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi skema RNG untuk memvalidasi berkas kontrol instalasi."

#. leap/yast2-instserver/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Installation Server Configuration and Management"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi dan Manajemen Server Instalasi"

#. leap/yast2-instserver/description
msgid ""
"This package allows you to configure an installation server suitable for "
"installaing SUSE Linux over the network. Currently FTP, HTTP and NFS sources "
"are supported."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini memungkinkan Anda untuk mengonfigurasi server instalasi yang "
"sesuai untuk menginstal SUSE Linux melalui jaringan. Saat ini sumber FTP, "
"HTTP, dan NFS didukung."

#. leap/yast2-iplb/summary
msgid "Configuration of iplb"
msgstr "Konfigurasi iplb"

#. leap/yast2-iplb/description
msgid ""
"YaST2 - Configuration of IP load balance.With this module you can configure "
"a IP load balance system, frequently used on high availability (HA) clusters."
msgstr ""
"YaST2 - Konfigurasi beban keseimbangan IP. Dengan modul ini Anda dapat "
"mengonfigurasi sistem beban keseimbangan IP, yang sering digunakan pada "
"kluster high availability (HA)."

#. leap/yast2-iscsi-client/summary
msgid "YaST2 - iSCSI Client Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Klien iSCSI"

#. leap/yast2-iscsi-client/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the YaST2 component for configuration of an iSCSI "
"client."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi klien iSCSI."

#. leap/yast2-iscsi-lio-server/summary
msgid "Configuration of iSCSI LIO target"
msgstr "Konfigurasi target iSCSI LIO"

#. leap/yast2-iscsi-lio-server/description
msgid "This package contains configuration of iSCSI LIO target"
msgstr "Paket ini berisi konfigurasi target iSCSI LIO"

#. leap/yast2-isns/summary
msgid "Configuration of isns"
msgstr "Konfigurasi isns"

#. leap/yast2-journal/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Reading of systemd journal"
msgstr "YaST2 - Pembacaan journal systemd"

#. leap/yast2-journal/description
msgid ""
"A YaST2 module to read the systemd journal in a convenient and user-friendly "
"way."
msgstr ""
"Modul YaST2 untuk membaca journal systemd dengan cara yang nyaman dan ramah "
"pengguna."

#. leap/yast2-kdump/summary
#. leap/yast2-kdump/description
msgid "Configuration of kdump"
msgstr "Konfigurasi kdump"

#. leap/yast2-ldap/summary
msgid "YaST2 - LDAP Agent"
msgstr "YaST2 - Agen LDAP"

#. leap/yast2-ldap/description
msgid ""
"This agent is used by various YaST2 modules to work with LDAP. It enables "
"searching the LDAP tree and adding/deleting/modifying items on an LDAP "
"server."
msgstr ""
"Agen ini digunakan oleh berbagai modul YaST2 untuk bekerja dengan LDAP. Ini "
"memungkinkan pencarian pohon LDAP dan menambah/menghapus/memodifikasi item "
"pada server LDAP."

#. leap/yast2/yast2-logs/summary
msgid "Scripts for handling YAST logs"
msgstr "Skrip untuk menangani log YAST"

#. leap/yast2/yast2-logs/description
msgid "This package contains scripts for handling YAST logs."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi skrip untuk menangani log YAST."

#. leap/yast2-mail/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Mail Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Email"

#. leap/yast2-mail/description
msgid ""
"The YaST2 component for mail configuration. It handles Postfix, Cyrus, "
"Amavis and Fetchmail."
msgstr ""
"Komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi email. Ini menangani Postfix, Cyrus, "
"Amavis, dan Fetchmail."

#. leap/yast2-metapackage-handler/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Easy Installation of Add-on RPMs using Metapackages"
msgstr "YaST2 - Instalasi Mudah RPM Tambahan menggunakan Metapackages"

#. leap/yast2-metapackage-handler/description
msgid ""
"With this technology users can install packages and add repositories with a "
"simple click on a link in a website."
msgstr ""
"Dengan teknologi ini pengguna dapat menginstal paket dan menambah repositori "
"hanya dengan satu klik pada tautan di sebuah situs web."

#. leap/yast2-migration/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Online migration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Migrasi daring"

#. leap/yast2-migration/description
msgid "This package contains the YaST2 component for online migration."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk migrasi daring."

#. leap/yast2-multipath/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Multipath Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Multipath"

#. leap/yast2-multipath/description
msgid ""
"Multipath I/O is a fault tolerance technique whereby there is more than one "
"physical path between the CPU in a computer system and its mass storage "
"devices through the buses, controllers, switches, and bridge devices "
"connecting them.\n"
"\n"
"You can configure your multipathed devices with this module."
msgstr ""
"Multipath I/O adalah teknik toleransi kesalahan di mana terdapat lebih dari "
"satu jalur fisik antara CPU dalam sistem komputer dan perangkat penyimpanan "
"massalnya melalui bus, pengontrol, sakelar, dan perangkat jembatan yang "
"menghubungkannya.\n"
"\n"
"Anda dapat mengonfigurasi perangkat multipath Anda dengan modul ini."

#. leap/yast2-network/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Network Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Jaringan"

#. leap/yast2-network/description
msgid "This package contains the YaST2 component for network configuration."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi jaringan."

#. leap/yast2-nfs-client/summary
msgid "YaST2 - NFS Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi NFS"

#. leap/yast2-nfs-client/description
msgid ""
"The YaST2 component for configuration of NFS. NFS stands for network file "
"system access. It allows access to files on remote machines."
msgstr ""
"Komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi NFS. NFS adalah singkatan dari network file "
"system access. Ini memungkinkan akses ke berkas pada mesin jarak jauh."

#. leap/yast2-nfs-server/yast2-nfs-common/summary
msgid "Configuration of NFS, common parts"
msgstr "Konfigurasi NFS, bagian umum"

#. leap/yast2-nfs-server/yast2-nfs-common/description
msgid "Common data for the NFS client and server modules"
msgstr "Data umum untuk modul klien dan server NFS"

#. leap/yast2-nfs-server/summary
msgid "YaST2 - NFS Server Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Server NFS"

#. leap/yast2-nfs-server/description
msgid ""
"The YaST2 component for configuration of an NFS server. NFS stands for "
"network file system access. It allows access to files on remote machines."
msgstr ""
"Komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi server NFS. NFS adalah singkatan dari "
"network file system access. Ini memungkinkan akses ke berkas pada mesin "
"jarak jauh."

#. leap/yast2-nis-client/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Network Information Services (NIS, YP) Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Network Information Services (NIS, YP)"

#. leap/yast2-nis-client/description
msgid ""
"The YaST2 component for NIS configuration. NIS is a service similar to "
"yellow pages."
msgstr ""
"Komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi NIS. NIS adalah layanan yang mirip dengan "
"yellow pages."

#. leap/yast2-nis-server/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Network Information Services (NIS) Server Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Server Network Information Services (NIS)"

#. leap/yast2-nis-server/description
msgid ""
"The YaST2 component for NIS server configuration. NIS is a service similar "
"to yellow pages."
msgstr ""
"Komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi server NIS. NIS adalah layanan yang mirip "
"dengan yellow pages."

#. leap/yast2-ntp-client/summary
msgid "YaST2 - NTP Client Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Klien NTP"

#. leap/yast2-ntp-client/description
msgid "This package contains the YaST2 component for NTP client configuration."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi klien NTP."

#. leap/yast2-online-update/summary
#. leap/yast2-online-update/yast2-online-update-frontend/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Online Update (YOU)"
msgstr "YaST2 - Online Update (YOU)"

#. leap/yast2-online-update/description
msgid ""
"YaST Online Update (YOU) provides a convenient way to download and install "
"security and other system updates. By default it uses the official SUSE "
"mirrors as the update sources, but it can also use local patch repositories "
"or patch CDs.\n"
"\n"
"This package provides the graphical user interface for YOU which can be used "
"with or without the X Window System. It can be started from the YaST control "
"center."
msgstr ""
"YaST Online Update (YOU) menyediakan cara yang nyaman untuk mengunduh dan "
"menginstal pembaruan keamanan dan pembaruan sistem lainnya. Secara default, "
"ia menggunakan mirror resmi SUSE sebagai sumber pembaruan, namun ia juga "
"dapat menggunakan repositori patch lokal atau CD patch.\n"
"\n"
"Paket ini menyediakan antarmuka pengguna grafis untuk YOU yang dapat "
"digunakan dengan atau tanpa X Window System. Ini dapat dimulai dari pusat "
"kontrol YaST."

#. leap/yast2-online-update-configuration/summary
msgid "Configuration of Online Update"
msgstr "Konfigurasi Online Update"

#. leap/yast2-online-update-configuration/description
msgid "Allows to configure automatic online update."
msgstr "Memungkinkan untuk mengonfigurasi pembaruan daring otomatis."

#. leap/yast2-online-update/yast2-online-update-frontend/description
msgid "Desktop files for YaST2 online update"
msgstr "Berkas desktop untuk pembaruan daring YaST2"

#. leap/yast2-packager/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Package Library"
msgstr "YaST2 - Pustaka Paket"

#. leap/yast2-packager/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the libraries and modules for software management."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi pustaka dan modul untuk manajemen perangkat lunak."

#. leap/yast2-pam/summary
msgid "YaST2 - PAM Agent"
msgstr "YaST2 - Agen PAM"

#. leap/yast2-pam/description
msgid "This agent is used by YaST2 to modify the PAM configuration files"
msgstr "Agen ini digunakan oleh YaST2 untuk memodifikasi berkas konfigurasi PAM"

#. leap/yast2-perl-bindings/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Perl Bindings"
msgstr "YaST2 - Binding Perl"

#. leap/yast2-perl-bindings/description
msgid ""
"This adds an embedded Perl interpreter to YaST2 as a plug-in (in other words "
"it will be loaded only if required). This is a very efficient way of calling "
"Perl from within YaST2 YCP scripts."
msgstr ""
"Ini menambahkan interpreter Perl tertanam ke YaST2 sebagai plug-in (dengan "
"kata lain, ia hanya akan dimuat jika diperlukan). Ini adalah cara yang "
"sangat efisien untuk memanggil Perl dari dalam skrip YCP YaST2."

#. leap/yast2-pkg-bindings/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Package Manager Access"
msgstr "YaST2 - Akses Manajer Paket"

#. leap/yast2-pkg-bindings/description
msgid ""
"This package contains a name space for accessing the package manager library "
"in YaST2."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi ruang nama untuk mengakses pustaka manajer paket di YaST2."

#. leap/yast2-pkg-bindings-devel-doc/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Documentation for yast2-pkg-bindings package"
msgstr "YaST2 - Dokumentasi untuk paket yast2-pkg-bindings"

#. leap/yast2-pkg-bindings-devel-doc/description
msgid ""
"This documenation package describes the package manager API (Pkg:: "
"namespace) used in YaST scripts. The documentation is autogenerated from the "
"pkg-bindings sources."
msgstr ""
"Paket dokumentasi ini menjelaskan API manajer paket (ruang nama Pkg::) yang "
"digunakan dalam skrip YaST. Dokumentasi ini dibuat secara otomatis dari "
"sumber pkg-bindings."

#. leap/yast2-printer/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Printer Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Pencetak"

#. leap/yast2-printer/description
msgid "This package contains the YaST2 component for printer configuration."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi pencetak."

#. leap/yast2-proxy/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Proxy Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Proksi"

#. leap/yast2-proxy/description
msgid "This package contains the YaST2 component for proxy configuration."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi proksi."

#. leap/yast2-python-bindings/yast2-python3-bindings/summary
msgid "Python3 bindings for the YaST platform"
msgstr "Binding Python3 untuk platform YaST"

#. leap/yast2-python-bindings/yast2-python3-bindings/description
msgid ""
"The bindings allow YaST modules to be written using the Python language and "
"also Python scripts can use YaST agents, APIs and modules."
msgstr ""
"Binding ini memungkinkan modul YaST ditulis menggunakan bahasa Python dan "
"skrip Python juga dapat menggunakan agen, API, dan modul YaST."

#. leap/yast2-rdp/summary
msgid "Setup Remote Desktop Protocol service for remote administration"
msgstr "Siapkan layanan Remote Desktop Protocol untuk administrasi jarak jauh"

#. leap/yast2-rdp/description
msgid ""
"Configure RDP (remote desktop protocol) daemon to allow remote system "
"administration."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasikan daemon RDP (remote desktop protocol) untuk memungkinkan "
"administrasi sistem jarak jauh."

#. leap/yast2-rear/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Rear - Relax and Recover"
msgstr "YaST2 - Rear - Relax and Recover"

#. leap/yast2-rear/description
msgid "The YaST2 component for configuring Rear - Relax and Recover Backup"
msgstr "Komponen YaST2 untuk mengonfigurasi Cadangan Rear - Relax and Recover"

#. leap/yast2-registration/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Registration Module"
msgstr "YaST2 - Modul Registrasi"

#. leap/yast2-registration/description
msgid ""
"The registration module to register products and/or to fetch an update "
"source (mirror) automatically."
msgstr ""
"Modul registrasi untuk mendaftarkan produk dan/atau mengambil sumber "
"pembaruan (mirror) secara otomatis."

#. leap/yast2-reipl/summary
msgid "YaST2 - IPL loader"
msgstr "YaST2 - Pemuat IPL"

#. leap/yast2-reipl/description
msgid "Module for loading IPL from running system on S/390"
msgstr "Modul untuk memuat IPL dari sistem yang sedang berjalan pada S/390"

#. leap/yast2-rmt/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Module to configure RMT"
msgstr "YaST2 - Modul untuk mengonfigurasi RMT"

#. leap/yast2-rmt/description
msgid ""
"Provides the YaST module to configure the Repository Mirroring Tool (RMT) "
"Server."
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan modul YaST untuk mengonfigurasi Server Repository Mirroring Tool "
"(RMT)."

#. leap/yast2-ruby-bindings/summary
msgid "Ruby bindings for the YaST platform"
msgstr "Binding Ruby untuk platform YaST"

#. leap/yast2-ruby-bindings/description
msgid ""
"The bindings allow YaST modules to be written using the Ruby language and "
"also Ruby scripts can use YaST agents, APIs and modules."
msgstr ""
"Binding ini memungkinkan modul YaST ditulis menggunakan bahasa Ruby dan "
"skrip Ruby juga dapat menggunakan agen, API, dan modul YaST."

#. leap/yast2-s390/summary
msgid "YaST2 - S/390 Specific Features Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Fitur Spesifik S/390"

#. leap/yast2-s390/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the YaST component for configuration of S/390-specific "
"features."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST untuk konfigurasi fitur spesifik S/390."

#. leap/yast2-samba-client/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Samba Client Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Klien Samba"

#. leap/yast2-samba-client/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the YaST2 component for configuration of an SMB "
"workgroup/domain and authentication against an SMB domain."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi workgroup/domain SMB dan "
"otentikasi terhadap domain SMB."

#. leap/yast2-samba-provision/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Samba AD DC provision"
msgstr "YaST2 - Provisioning Samba AD DC"

#. leap/yast2-samba-provision/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the YaST2 component to configure samba as an Active "
"Directory (TM) Domain Controller."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk mengonfigurasi samba sebagai "
"Pengontrol Domain Active Directory (TM)."

#. leap/yast2-samba-server/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Samba Server Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Server Samba"

#. leap/yast2-samba-server/description
msgid ""
"This package contains the YaST2 component for Samba server configuration."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi komponen YaST2 untuk konfigurasi server Samba."

#. leap/yast2-scanner/summary
msgid "YaST2 - Scanner Configuration"
msgstr "YaST2 - Konfigurasi Pemindai"

#. leap/yast2-scanner/description
msgid ""
"This package provides support for the configuration of USB scanners, SCSI "
"scanners, scanners in HP all-in-one devices, and scanning via network (i.e. "
"use a remote scanner via another host in the network).\n"
"\n"
"Parallel port scanners and network scanners (i.e. a scanner which is "
"directly accessible in the network) cannot be configured with this tool, "
"except for such scanners in HP all-in-one devices. Usually those devices "
"must be configured manually. For more information see http://www.sane-"
"project.org/ and the documentation in the package \"sane-backends\"."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini menyediakan dukungan untuk konfigurasi pemindai USB, pemindai "
"SCSI, pemindai pada perangkat all-in-one HP, dan pemindaian melalui jaringan "
"(yaitu menggunakan pemindai jarak jauh melalui host lain dalam jaringan).\n"
"\n"
"Pemindai port paralel dan pemindai jaringan (yaitu pemindai yang dapat "
"diakses langsung di jaringan) tidak dapat dikonfigurasi dengan alat ini, "
"kecuali untuk pemindai serupa pada perangkat all-in-one HP. Biasanya "
"perangkat tersebut harus dikonfigurasi secara manual. Untuk informasi lebih "
"lanjut lihat [http://www.sane-project.org/](http://www.sane-project.org/) "
"dan dokumentasi dalam paket \"sane-backends\"."

